WEBVTT

00:02.066 --> 00:04.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Moving and
shaking today in the White
House communications staff.

00:04.066 --> 00:08.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Sean Spicer resigned as press
secretary after just six months,
saying the president needs

00:08.300 --> 00:10.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a -- quote -- "clean slate."

00:10.333 --> 00:14.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But it was widely reported that
he objected to the naming of
Wall Street financier Anthony

00:14.133 --> 00:16.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Scaramucci as
communications director.

00:16.766 --> 00:20.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
