Scaramucci sought to play
down talk of any discord.

00:20.866 --> 00:23.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANTHONY SCARAMUCCI, Incoming
White House Communications
Director: For me, as
it relates to Sean, it

00:23.800 --> 00:27.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
speaks volumes to who he
is as a human being, who
he is as a team player.

00:27.733 --> 00:29.766 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
OK?

00:29.766 --> 00:31.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
