Anthony's coming in, let me
clear the slate for Anthony.

00:31.800 --> 00:34.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I do appreciate that about
Sean, and I love him for it.

00:34.866 --> 00:37.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But I don't have any
friction with Sean.

00:37.266 --> 00:41.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
