Scaramucci also named
Spicer's deputy, Sarah
Huckabee Sanders, to be the

00:41.333 --> 00:43.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
new press secretary.

00:43.466 --> 00:46.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
