00:58.133 --> 01:01.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mueller is investigating Russian
meddling in the 2016 election.

01:01.566 --> 01:05.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The White House would neither
confirm nor deny the reports.

01:05.000 --> 01:09.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The president's lead lawyer did
deny a Washington Post account
that they're examining whether

01:09.700 --> 01:13.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Mr. Trump could pardon
relatives, aides
and even himself.

01:13.666 --> 01:18.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
We will take a closer
look at all of this
after the news summary.

01:18.000 --> 01:21.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Israeli-Palestinian
tensions erupted into
street battles today between
police and protesters

01:21.933 --> 01:23.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in Jerusalem and the West Bank.

01:23.866 --> 01:28.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
