killed, and nearly 400 hurt.

01:28.700 --> 01:33.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Exploding stun grenades
drowned out Friday prayers in
Jerusalem, as ambulance sirens

01:34.166 --> 01:36.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
wailed.

01:36.300 --> 01:40.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
