both Muslims and Jews.

01:43.466 --> 01:46.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator):
This place is made
for worshipping God.

01:46.833 --> 01:48.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
