third holiest site in Islam, and
the Dome of the Rock, they're

02:07.366 --> 02:12.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
bordered by the Western Wall,
the holiest site in Judaism.

02:12.000 --> 02:14.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
