ever since the shooting.

02:14.233 --> 02:18.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Overnight, the streets of
Jerusalem's Old City were
filled with protesters throwing

02:18.566 --> 02:22.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
stones and security forces
firing back with grenades.

02:22.300 --> 02:27.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
