blocked busloads of Muslims
traveling to Jerusalem.

02:34.300 --> 02:36.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICKY ROSENFELD, Israeli
Police Spokesman: The security
measures will continue in and

02:36.400 --> 02:40.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
around the area of the Old City
and the Temple Mount, in order
to prevent any further terrorist

02:40.800 --> 02:43.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
attacks.

02:43.366 --> 02:46.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But the
grand mufti of Jerusalem
rallied thousands of
Muslims to pray outside

02:46.200 --> 02:49.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the gates of the old city, under
the watch of Israeli forces.

02:49.733 --> 02:52.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
