long test of wills.

02:52.033 --> 02:55.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMIN AL-HUSSEINI, Grand Mufti of
Jerusalem (through translator):
We do accept any restrictions

02:55.366 --> 02:57.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
on the door of the
Al-Aqsa Mosque.

02:57.466 --> 03:02.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Therefore, all the Palestinian
people reject these gates
and refuse to accept or enter

03:02.200 --> 03:04.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
through them.

03:04.266 --> 03:07.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The violence
broke out after prayers, and
spilled over to towns across

03:07.966 --> 03:10.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the West Bank.

03:10.500 --> 03:13.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
