turned to grief, as
mourners held a funeral
for one of the Palestinian

03:14.433 --> 03:16.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
dead.

03:16.533 --> 03:18.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
