three Israelis to death
in a West Bank settlement.

03:18.933 --> 03:23.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tonight, Palestinian President
Mahmoud Abbas announced he's
freezing contacts with Israel

03:23.700 --> 03:25.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
on all levels.

