Greek island of Kos, and the
Turkish tourist hub of Bodrum.

04:46.800 --> 04:50.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Nearly 500 people were injured,
and the tremor caused heavy
damage to buildings, roads and

04:51.366 --> 04:52.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
historical sites.

04:52.900 --> 04:54.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
