but got stranded.

04:57.600 --> 05:02.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
We were woken up at
1:30 in the morning.

05:03.466 --> 05:04.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We were wondering what happened.

05:04.466 --> 05:05.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Everything was shaking.

05:05.833 --> 05:08.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
