it to fall on our heads.

05:15.733 --> 05:16.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Everyone was out in the street.

05:16.966 --> 05:18.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It was a massive panic.

05:18.733 --> 05:21.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
