and lamps were upside down.

05:21.600 --> 05:25.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The two
people killed were identified as
tourists from Turkey and Sweden.

05:25.700 --> 05:30.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
